title: Estrada leads Blue Jays over Royals 7-1 to force ALCS Game 6
text: BING NEWS: Estrada leads Blue Jays over Royals 7-1 to force ALCS Game 6 TORONTO — Marco Estrada pitched one-hit ball into the eighth inning, giving Toronto's tattered bullpen a rest and leading the Blue Jays over the Kansas City Royals 7-1 Wednesday to close to 3-2 in the American League Championship Series.
